{"tid":628920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內地蘋果手機殼「有毒」或傷腎致癌","createTime":"2018-04-14T09:31:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T09:51:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cfd398b79e1c69a4cbff38a327fa047bb09f642c","tid":628920,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T09:31:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180414/20361091?_ga=2.104451968.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180414%2F20361091%3F_ga%3D2.104451968.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=y2KIXyCTZjw%2B5kY2bIgPD26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=3cb9668f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180414%2F20361091%3F_ga%3D2.104451968.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=3a5debac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180414/20361091?_ga=2.104451968.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n內地蘋果手機殼「有毒」或傷腎致癌<br />\n<br />\n47.8K<br />\n要聞<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】深圳市消委會發表報告，抽查市面暢銷的30款手機殼，發現名廠蘋果、小米在內的5款手機殼，含有毒或致癌物質，包括一款在港有售的蘋果手機殼，驗出多環芳烴含量超標50倍；另一款女士最愛的「水鑽閃粉彩膜」手機殼，鉛含量更超標1,550倍，攝入過量有可能傷害腦細胞及引致腎衰竭。<br />\n<br />\n國家工信部資料顯示，內地約14.2億手機用戶，當中約10億人有使用手機殼習慣，但內地尚無標準及法例監管。深圳市消委會參考歐盟、德國、美國等安全標準，測試市面28個牌子共30款手機殼，前日公佈測試結果。<br />\n<br />\n在201項化學物質測試中，23款樣本被評「超出國際一流」標準，沒驗出有害化學物質，當中13款更通過老化測試，獲五星評價，另有兩款驗出塑化劑及多環芳烴但未超標，獲評為三星。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180414/large/a0804a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180414%2Flarge%2Fa0804a.gif&h=fbb774b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蘋果MR672FE/A型手機殼<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n水鑽閃粉彩膜鉛超標1,550倍<br />\n<br />\n測試發現，蘋果及小米等5款產品，驗出有毒物質超標而不獲評級。蘋果手機殼多環芳烴含量為94mg/kg，超標近50倍，不合格產品型號為MR672FE/A，適用於iPhone 7/8，在港官網售價258元。<br />\n<br />\n小米手機殼塑化劑含量超標0.1%。樣本中超標最離譜的，是名為躍寧「水鑽閃粉彩膜」的手機殼，鉛、塑化劑、短鏈氯化石蠟超標，粉色水鑽中鉛含量超標1,550倍。<br />\n<br />\n中新網昨引述小米的聲明，指試驗參考的是歐盟標準針對「兒童用品和兒童護理用品──餐具和餵養器具」，不適用手機殼。研究表明，攝入塑化劑可令女性內分泌系統紊亂，影響生育及兒童生殖系統。<br />\n<br />\n多環芳烴是國際公認的強致癌物質，能引發皮膚癌、肺癌及肝癌等病變。鉛元素直接傷害腦細胞，破壞骨骼及引腎衰竭。<br />\n<br />\n香港急症科醫學院臨牀毒理專科委員會主席劉飛龍稱，化學物質對人體產生的毒性，要視乎接觸的劑量而定，例如不少物品會含微量的鉛，但非一定會引起中毒。<br />\n<br />\n■記者廖智廣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180414/large/a0804b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180414%2Flarge%2Fa0804b.gif&h=75387355&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b427ae4eb5bc1b4442f6817ae222c9acf49a304","tid":628920,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T09:36:26.000Z","msg":"樓主硬膠泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=3124d977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ff15f2d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/201929_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F10%2F201929_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=27225035&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da8bd929011c9f2927e6c838574b286402a5f9c5","tid":628920,"uid":49588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T09:51:40.000Z","msg":"內你老母臭晒！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=